summary:
I am known for my enthusiastic and driven personality, and as someone who is able to empower
people. By bringing energy, communicating in a direct manner, and sharing my ideas and thoughts with the people around me, I inspire and motivate my team in a completely authentic way. 

My love for football and desire to deliver quality is a big part of my way of working. I have a clear vision and love to get people on board, so we can reach our common goals together ‚öΩÔ∏è

Biggest Achievements and main results:
‚û°Ô∏è  Participation in the European Championship 2021 final tournament, part of the technical
staff
‚û°Ô∏è  Successfully trained a new generation of football trainers and coaches (2017)
‚û°Ô∏è  Qualification for the UEFA elite national U19 tournament (Oct2017- Oct 2018)
‚û°Ô∏è  Qualification for European Championship final round U17, Bulgaria (2015)
‚û°Ô∏è  Qualification for European Championship final round U17, Malta (2014)
‚û°Ô∏è  2nd Place European Championship UEFA U17, Malta (2014)
‚û°Ô∏è  9th Place Ajax Cape Town (first team)
‚û°Ô∏è  Ajax Youth Team Championships
‚û°Ô∏è  Tournament, Cup and Supercup Ajax Youth Teams win
‚û°Ô∏èOne of the results that stands out most, is the transition of talent at Ajax Cape Town from the youth academy to the first team. Not only as part of the selection, but also playing weekly
in the first team and numerous representative teams in South Africa

If you would like to get in touch for new opportunities, please contact me via LinkedInüì© 
I have worldwide availability and am open to discuss  new opportunities.
